# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo so diffs stay clean on Windows.
# Keeps line-ending noise out of `git diff`, so you can see exactly which
# files you changed and need to copy back into Figma Make.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Treat image assets as binary (never line-ending converted).
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.ico binary
